{"tid":833612,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「傳愛暖萬心」大家入黎講返句中秋節快樂啦","createTime":"2018-09-23T15:44:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T23:28:00.000Z","uid":6005,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9398551dbbf318508ba0beffeb3514e555f1c65a","tid":833612,"uid":6005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:44:28.000Z","msg":"適逢中秋節，大家都免不了同屋企人一齊食燈籠<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、玩月餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，享受天倫之樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。但大家有冇諗過個嗰大時大節重要返到夜一夜、比客屌老母嘅人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，所以我決定中秋節當日會同所有m記姐姐、譚仔阿姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等服務性行業嘅人，比錢嗰時都講返句中秋節快樂，等大家知道這個城市還有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想問吓大家有冇興趣跟上<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：大愛撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c04c5c60649e035ed5debd6e26dc45e377764184","tid":833612,"uid":6005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T16:11:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07a13581c8889ac1d7342627dcbd10f576f0474e","tid":833612,"uid":99344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T16:21:45.000Z","msg":"見冇人覆你，中秋節快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a0ac6e440419c3ce5a47441cdb2e1993385758","tid":833612,"uid":210088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c04c5c60